'''退货授权'''(Return merchandise authorization，簡稱RMA)是指顧客在[[产品|产品]][[保修期|保修期]]内退货以获得退款或更换以及维修產品的流程。顧客和商家可以商討如何处理产品，可以是退款、更换产品或维修产品<ref>Dana Dubbs, “Many (unhappy) Returns”, Operations & Fulfillment, Vol. 9, No. 3, March 2001.</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=What is return merchandise authorization (RMA)? - Definition from WhatIs.com|url=http://whatis.techtarget.com/definition/return-merchandise-authorization-RMA|publisher=}}</ref>。

